
GOAL: xkcd, text similarity between comics

1.) get all xkcd transcripts from explain xkcd
	- different post-processing: remove characters, use explainations
2.) calculate cosine similarity between texts
	- article with different vectors
3.) text clustering with Metric Multi-Dimensional Scaling (MDS)
	- use scikit-learn

- - - - -

xkcd_data_sourcer.py : a file to extract the text from pages on the 'explain xkcd' html pages

@ USING
- requests : get html
- BeautifulSoup : prettify html
- lxml : lxml is the most feature-rich and easy-to-use library for processing XML and HTML in the Python language.
